data.description: This stunning two-story home nestled on 1.1 acres of serene countryside. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 1/2 bathrooms, a light and airy residence offers an abundance of living spaces and dining rooms, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time. Step into the open kitchen with ample counter space. The inviting atmosphere flows seamlessly into the dining area, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. Indulge in relaxation and entertainment in the game room, a versatile space that can be transformed to suit your needs. Whether it's a cozy movie night or a lively game of pool, this room is sure to be a favorite gathering spot for all. Take in the breathtaking views from two balconies, perfect for morning coffee or evening stargazing. The expansive land surrounding the property offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities and potential expansion. Embracing sustainability, with a well and 14 solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency and reduced utility costs. Schedule a tour today.
